<section class="section-pad" id="how">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="kicker">Up and running in 2 minutes</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Three steps to a <span class="accent">calmer browser</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step glass reveal">
        <div class="step-connector"></div>
        <span class="step-num">1</span>
        <h3>Add to Chrome</h3>
        <p>Install Cuewise free from the Chrome Web Store. No account required — it just works on your very next tab.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step glass reveal">
        <div class="step-connector"></div>
        <span class="step-num">2</span>
        <h3>Make it yours</h3>
        <p>Pick a theme — Purple, Forest, Rose or Glass — choose your quote categories, and set the density that feels right.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step glass reveal">
        <span class="step-num">3</span>
        <h3>Open a new tab</h3>
        <p>That's it. Every new tab now greets you with wisdom, your focus, and a quiet nudge toward what matters.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
